Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 还要饭团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:47.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:48.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,奶奶什么都不和我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:03.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,能和夏月一起生活 一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样对我来说就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:24.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我没能帮上我最爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想被那个人夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:34.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以一直努力 努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是星菜夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从很久以前就是鬼丸小姐粉丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很久以前?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别说的我好像很老一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我和你是同龄人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是完全没帮上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,尽是被骂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,其实她很温柔 是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只是看起来很冷酷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,既然要背负女主角党的名字组成组合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就不能有半吊子的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:12.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,两个人组成了With这个团体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为了追赶她 拼命努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:27.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想成为她的力量
