Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想要的只有这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:51.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,仅仅这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真希望她能知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事的 你们的心连在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:08.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月你是最清楚不过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:15.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,重新再一次相信她不也很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:27.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,Smile♥X 啊 Smile♥X
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可恶 还是Cherry7领先啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,Smile♥X 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,加油啊 Smile♥X 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:28.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 现在不是哭的时候 快给她们加油啊
