Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,1950万票
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:12.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,Smile♥X 获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,开始记者会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:29.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员们 就趁现在好好高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您辛苦了 万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:41.17,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听说接下来樱庭总理要在官邸举行记者会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:53.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我刚刚在电视上观看了Cherry7和Smile♥X的表演对决直播
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:58.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有了一些想法 临时决定召开记者会
